 complete solution that will quickly maximize the benefits of moving to the Cloud.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Your cloud implementation plan includes an understanding of your current IT infrastructure, key business objectives and impact, a detailed cloud solution design and migration plan that will ensure a smooth transition to the cloud.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"=""><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Cloud Workspace</strong></p><ul style="margin: 21px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;"=""><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">The Cloud Workspace is your virtual office wherever you are. AWT Cloud Workspace delivers a configurable Cloud Workspace environment, allowing you to control business applications and data with secure access for all your employees from anywhere, from any device, via any internet or private connection.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Delivers a cost effective IT experience, with 24/7/365 technical support for a fixed monthly fee per user eliminating capital expenditures for servers, networking technology, and software.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" brea