change</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"=""><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Cloud DR</strong></p><ul style="margin: 21px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;"=""><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">AWT Cloud Disaster Recovery solution is a fully managed Disaster Recovery Service with customized email event notification, which secures your business data, applications and operating systems by continuously replicating your primary servers to a secondary data center.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Full server replication protects both physical and virtual servers. Hardware and application independent – supporting your Hardware and Software configuration.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"=""><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Server Management</strong></p><ul style="margin: 21px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;"=""><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">AWT provides advanced server management and monitoring tools, and our engineers can remotely perform a majority of the server management functions you might provide onsite.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">This service provides you with real-time awareness of the state of your network through our web interface tool.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">AWT technical teams and security experts monitor your servers 24×7 and are in position to handle any issues that might occur—no matter what time of day or what day of the year and stay engaged until the problem is resolved to minimize any impact on your business.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"=""><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Network Management</strong></p><ul style="margin: 21px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;"=""><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Our Network Operations Center (NOC) enables us to continuously monitor and proactively manage your network devices, including network routers, network switches, load balancers, WAN accelerators, SSL VPN concentrators, and wireless access points.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">This service provides you with real-time awareness of the state of your network through our web interface tool. This way, you can know as soon as we do if your servers, applications and IT services are experiencing outages, performance degradation or approaching critical availability thresholds.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">AWT technical teams and security experts monitor your network devices 24×7 and are in place to handle any issues that might occur – no matter what time of day or what day of the year, and stay engaged until the problem is resolved.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"=""><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Cloud Migration</strong></p><ul style="margin: 21px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;"=""><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Moving your IT environment to the Cloud can position your business for increased IT agility, reduced operating expense and tremendous improvements in your security and disaster recovery capabilities.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">AWT’s Cloud Migration Service assures that your business will have a seamless server migration to the AWT Cloud, and our team of experienced Professional Services Consultants and Cloud Engineering Consultants will ensure the service meets or exceeds your expectations.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Our team of experienced consultants and engineers supports your migration to mitigate risk, not only during the transitional period but also during the day-to-day operations of your IT environment.</li><li style="line-height: 21px; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" margin:="" 0px="" 5px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" inherit;="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Fully managed migration process that expedites your time to value, minimizes disruptions to your business and your IT staff.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 21px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: " open="" sans",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" line-height:="" 21px;="" padding:="" 0px;="" color:="" rgb(84,="" 84,="" 84);="" word-wrap:="" break-word;"="">Please&nbsp;<a title="Contact" href="https://www.accessworld.net/products-and-services/contact" style="color: rgb(33, 150, 243); margin: 0px 0px 21px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-wrap: break-word;">contact us</a>&nbsp;to discuss your IT needs.</p></h4>',
